data.description: This stunning custom-built home boasts an open-concept design and is a true masterpiece. This home offers the perfect blend of modern elegance & comfort. Living room features 2-story soaring ceilings & the fireplace adds warmth and ambiance. This space effortlessly opens up to the outdoor living area. Well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream. A convenient butler's pantry, cleverly hidden behind frosted sliding glass doors, offers extra storage and prep space. Conveniently located off the kitchen, you'll find a laundry & mudroom, home office, & a half bath for your guests' convenience. The library boasts custom built-ins and a private full bath, making it a versatile space. Primary bedroom, with an ensuite bath & custom closet, is situated on the main level. Upstairs loft living area overlooks the living room & perfectly accommodates 3 additional bedrooms. Private outdoor living area designed for entertaining & relaxation features a well-equipped outdoor kitchen, hot tub & fire pit.
